# A usable inner PK lookup has first refusal and remains index-nested-loop.
query ITTII nosort
EXPLAIN SELECT l.id, r.id FROM hx_l l JOIN hx_r r ON r.id = l.k
----
0
Nested Loop
inner; on:conjuncts=1
2
11
1
Scan hx_l
Full scan; touched=2
2
3
1
Scan hx_r
Index-nested-loop PK bound: id = join; touched=1
2
4

